  <para id="para-00010">The <term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00021">American Heart Association</term> provides an <link url="https://openstax.org/r/watchlearnlive">interactive library on the anatomy of blood pressure</link>. The library includes images and topics to explore such as the anatomy of blood pressure, high blood pressure and the cardiovascular system, and a blood pressure test.</para>

  <media alt="atoms_isotopes">
