  <para id="para-00011">This video with Dr. Leslie Thomas, MD, a nephrologist at Mayo Clinic, discusses facts, questions, and answers about blood pressure to help clients better understand hypertension. The video talks about hypertension, risk factors, symptoms, diagnosis, treatment options, and coping methods to manage the disease process.</para>
